Introduction

PoshGirls-J (Korean: 파시걸스-제이) was the first sub-unit of the girl group PoshGirls, consisting of the Japanese members. They made their debut on June 24, 2022 in Japan with their first mini album Lali:lala. The group disbanded on March 1, 2023.
